is child theme "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
==============================================================

NAME
----

is child theme - Whether a child theme is in use.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Whether a child theme is in use.

USAGE
-----

` <?php is_child_theme(); ?> `

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `` `(bool)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   true if a child theme is in use, false otherwise.

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [3.0](/Version_3.0 "Version 3.0")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`is_child_theme()` is located in `wp-includes/theme.php`

